{"tid":1303212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施政報告公眾諮詢展開　特首稱與團隊虛心聆聽市民聲音","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:14:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0db700f28e3ae849d532445b40ffbfe4a46b1ced","tid":1303212,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:33:45.000Z","msg":"政府今日起展開2019年《施政報告》公眾諮詢，行政長官林鄭月娥、政務司司長張建宗、財政司司長陳茂波將陸續與不同界別人士會面，聽取意見。<br />\n<br />\n市民可透過《施政報告》網站、社交媒體專頁、電郵、電話或傳真提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，要持續發展經濟，改善民生，需要一起籌謀，同心協力。邀各市民就《施政報告》發表意見，集思廣益，制訂切合市民需要的政策措施，並會與團隊虛心聆聽廣大市民的聲音，在第3份《施政報告》中作出回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467631-20190710.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467631-20190710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=fac63e76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467631-20190710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9e336cf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467631-20190710.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府反擊戰即將展開</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbc434deb53dd258cc49a6f6fa841ed95e6ced0","tid":1303212,"uid":83487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"連登巴絲ready好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3333d594b4fed6990cc84508e6b80bcec3cf0b73","tid":1303212,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3556b9b92e2582f87f9fa2e980b96d4cdb378050","tid":1303